<item>
            <title>[LU-12256] Use D_NETTRACE for LND code, and D_NET for LNet code</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12256</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be useful to be able to toggle the LND and LNet debug output independently. Sometimes the LND output is not interesting when looking at issues in the LNet layer. This is especially true as complex new features are being added at the the LNet layer (Multi-Rail, Dynamic Discovery, LNet Health, etc.).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently, only kgnilnd utilizes the D_NETTRACE mask, so I suggest we switch all LNDs to use this mask for their debug output.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="55545">LU-12256</key>
            <summary>Use D_NETTRACE for LND code, and D_NET for LNet code</summary>
