                            <comment id="246726" author="hornc" created="Sun, 5 May 2019 15:51:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ideally I think we&apos;d have three masks available. D_NET for general LNet layer messages, D_LND, for general LND layer messages, and D_NETTRACE which would be equivalent to the D_TRACE but employed only at the LNet and LND layer to show function entry/exit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
